{"snp1.6:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 1.6 ","snp1.6:0.2":"Parabhavasutta ","snp1.6:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","snp1.6:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame. ","snp1.6:1.3":"Atha kho annatara devata abhikkantaya rattiya abhikkantavanna kevalakappam jetavanam obhasetva yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam atthasi. ","snp1.6:1.4":"Ekamantam thita kho sa devata bhagavantam gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","snp1.6:2.1":"“Parabhavantam purisam, ","snp1.6:2.2":"mayam pucchama gotama; ","snp1.6:2.3":"Bhavantam putthumagamma, ","snp1.6:2.4":"kim parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:3.1":"“Suvijano bhavam hoti, ","snp1.6:3.2":"suvijano parabhavo; ","snp1.6:3.3":"Dhammakamo bhavam hoti, ","snp1.6:3.4":"dhammadessi parabhavo”. ","snp1.6:4.1":"“Iti hetam vijanama, ","snp1.6:4.2":"pathamo so parabhavo; ","snp1.6:4.3":"Dutiyam bhagava bruhi, ","snp1.6:4.4":"kim parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:5.1":"“Asantassa piya honti, ","snp1.6:5.2":"sante na kurute piyam; ","snp1.6:5.3":"Asatam dhammam roceti, ","snp1.6:5.4":"tam parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:6.1":"“Iti hetam vijanama, ","snp1.6:6.2":"dutiyo so parabhavo; ","snp1.6:6.3":"Tatiyam bhagava bruhi, ","snp1.6:6.4":"kim parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:7.1":"“Niddasili sabhasili, ","snp1.6:7.2":"anutthata ca yo naro; ","snp1.6:7.3":"Alaso kodhapannano, ","snp1.6:7.4":"tam parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:8.1":"“Iti hetam vijanama, ","snp1.6:8.2":"tatiyo so parabhavo; ","snp1.6:8.3":"Catuttham bhagava bruhi, ","snp1.6:8.4":"kim parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:9.1":"“Yo mataram pitaram va, ","snp1.6:9.2":"jinnakam gatayobbanam; ","snp1.6:9.3":"Pahu santo na bharati, ","snp1.6:9.4":"tam parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:10.1":"“Iti hetam vijanama, ","snp1.6:10.2":"catuttho so parabhavo; ","snp1.6:10.3":"Pancamam bhagava bruhi, ","snp1.6:10.4":"kim parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:11.1":"“Yo brahmanam samanam va, ","snp1.6:11.2":"Annam vapi vanibbakam; ","snp1.6:11.3":"Musavadena vanceti, ","snp1.6:11.4":"Tam parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:12.1":"“Iti hetam vijanama, ","snp1.6:12.2":"Pancamo so parabhavo; ","snp1.6:12.3":"Chatthamam bhagava bruhi, ","snp1.6:12.4":"Kim parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:13.1":"“Pahutavitto puriso, ","snp1.6:13.2":"Sahiranno sabhojano; ","snp1.6:13.3":"Eko bhunjati saduni, ","snp1.6:13.4":"Tam parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:14.1":"“Iti hetam vijanama, ","snp1.6:14.2":"Chatthamo so parabhavo; ","snp1.6:14.3":"Sattamam bhagava bruhi, ","snp1.6:14.4":"Kim parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:15.1":"“Jatitthaddho dhanatthaddho, ","snp1.6:15.2":"Gottatthaddho ca yo naro; ","snp1.6:15.3":"Sannatim atimanneti, ","snp1.6:15.4":"Tam parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:16.1":"“Iti hetam vijanama, ","snp1.6:16.2":"Sattamo so parabhavo; ","snp1.6:16.3":"Atthamam bhagava bruhi, ","snp1.6:16.4":"Kim parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:17.1":"“Itthidhutto suradhutto, ","snp1.6:17.2":"Akkhadhutto ca yo naro; ","snp1.6:17.3":"Laddham laddham vinaseti, ","snp1.6:17.4":"Tam parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:18.1":"“Iti hetam vijanama, ","snp1.6:18.2":"Atthamo so parabhavo; ","snp1.6:18.3":"Navamam bhagava bruhi, ","snp1.6:18.4":"Kim parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:19.1":"“Sehi darehi asantuttho, ","snp1.6:19.2":"Vesiyasu padussati; ","snp1.6:19.3":"Dussati paradaresu, ","snp1.6:19.4":"Tam parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:20.1":"“Iti hetam vijanama, ","snp1.6:20.2":"Navamo so parabhavo; ","snp1.6:20.3":"Dasamam bhagava bruhi, ","snp1.6:20.4":"Kim parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:21.1":"“Atitayobbano poso, ","snp1.6:21.2":"Aneti timbarutthanim; ","snp1.6:21.3":"Tassa issa na supati, ","snp1.6:21.4":"Tam parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:22.1":"“Iti hetam vijanama, ","snp1.6:22.2":"Dasamo so parabhavo; ","snp1.6:22.3":"Ekadasamam bhagava bruhi, ","snp1.6:22.4":"Kim parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:23.1":"“Itthim sondim vikiranim, ","snp1.6:23.2":"Purisam vapi tadisam; ","snp1.6:23.3":"Issariyasmim thapeti, ","snp1.6:23.4":"Tam parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:24.1":"“Iti hetam vijanama, ","snp1.6:24.2":"Ekadasamo so parabhavo; ","snp1.6:24.3":"Dvadasamam bhagava bruhi, ","snp1.6:24.4":"Kim parabhavato mukham”. ","snp1.6:25.1":"“Appabhogo mahatanho, ","snp1.6:25.2":"Khattiye jayate kule; ","snp1.6:25.3":"So ca rajjam patthayati, ","snp1.6:25.4":"Tam parabhavato mukham. ","snp1.6:26.1":"Ete parabhave loke, ","snp1.6:26.2":"Pandito samavekkhiya; ","snp1.6:26.3":"Ariyo dassanasampanno, ","snp1.6:26.4":"Sa lokam bhajate sivan”ti. ","snp1.6:26.5":"Parabhavasuttam chattham. "}